         <property name="plainText">
          <string>Chord morph stations: define the location of control points along blade span in [0 1] for chord morphing, e.g. 0.5 means the control point at the middle of blade length;

Twist morph stations: Similar with the Chord but for twist morphing;

Thickness morph stations: Similar with the Chord but for thickness morphing;

Upper and lower limits: the lower limit of each control points in [0 1]. Format: [[[lower limit of chord morph],[lower limit of twist morph],[lower limit of thckness morph]],[[Upper limit of chord morph],[Upper limit of twist morph],[Upper limit of thckness morph]]]
</string>
         </property>
        </widget>
