Thickness of 9 stations (the only available option currently): Define sacaling factor for 9 pre-defined stations;

Upper and lower limits: the lower limit of each control points in [0 1]. Format: [[-0.5, 0.5],[-0.5,0.5]] means changing within the 0.5 and 1.5 of original values; A list for each morphing in sequence and seperated by semicolon;
